file: package.json
purpose: Node.js project manifest for a steno-theory compiler that transforms `.steno` source files into Plover JSON dictionaries. Defines build, test, and typecheck scripts using native TypeScript stripping (no bundler).
invariants:
  - All scripts run via `node --experimental-strip-types`; no transpile/bundle step.
external_deps:
  - vitest: test runner and watch mode.
functions: